subject: Missing Plus X Pedals in delivery
description_text:
Hello, today I received just the VAM Pros that I ordered but I haven't
received the Plus X pedals. Since they seemingly came in a different
package. But I don't have a second tracking number. I was wondering where I
would find that or if there was an issue.

I reached out previously on a different ticket but never received a
response on that one. I added a comment but didn't know if that was the
best way to reach out so I figured I should open a new ticket since it was
a new issue.

I also reached out on an Amazon seller message. I look forward to hearing
from you.

Thank you.
